==English==

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɪf|-ɪf]]

===Verb===
to '''sniff'''
# to make a short, [[audible]] [[inhalation]], through the [[nose]], as if to [[smell]] something.
# to be [[dismissive]] or [[contemptuous]] of something.

====Translations====
*French: [[renifler]]
*German: [[schnüffeln]]
*Hungarian: [[szimatol]]
*Italian: [[annusare]]
*Spanish: [[husmear]], [[sorber]]
*Russian: [[принюхиваться]]

===Noun===
'''sniff'''
# an [[instance]] of sniffing.

